## Development

This project uses an AI-assisted autonomous development workflow powered by GitHub Copilot.

### Quick Start

1. Open this repo in VS Code
2. Ensure GitHub Copilot is active
3. Open Chat (Ctrl+Shift+I) and select the **autonomous-builder** agent
4. The agent will read `roadmap/CURRENT-STATE.md` and continue from where it left off

### Manual Development Cycle

Use `/` prompts in Copilot Chat for human-driven development:

```
/phase-plan → /implementation-plan → /implementation-plan-review → /implement → /code-review → /security-audit → /phase-complete
```

See [.github/prompts/PROMPT-GUIDE.md](.github/prompts/PROMPT-GUIDE.md) for details.

